{
  "_comment": [
    "Word count with fully partitioner-managed placement and topology.",
    "",
    "placement:'all' nodes are expanded to one copy per machine automatically.",
    "  load       \u2192 load_0, load_1            (each reads the locally staged corpus)",
    "  distribute \u2192 distribute_0, distribute_1  (fan-out base slot: out_base=30)",
    "  map_n      \u2192 map_n_0_{0..9}, map_n_1_{0..9}  (fanout:10 applied per machine)",
    "  aggregate  \u2192 aggregate_0, aggregate_1  (each collects its machine's map outputs)",
    "",
    "shared_inputs is auto-derived from the 'load' Input node; no need to declare it.",
    "",
    "Auto-placed nodes: aggregate_global, reduce, save.",
    "  placement_policy controls where these land (default: pack = colocate on fewest hosts).",
    "",
    "Available placement_policy values:",
    "  'balanced'  \u2014 spread proportionally across all hosts",
    "  'pack'      \u2014 colocate on fewest hosts (default when field is omitted)",
    "  'spread'    \u2014 at most one auto-node per host",
    "  { 'type': 'weighted', 'weights': [0.8, 0.2] }  \u2014 explicit capacity ratio",
    "  { 'type': 'balanced', 'per_host_limit': 4 }    \u2014 balanced with a sandbox cap"
  ],
  "shm_path_prefix": "/dev/shm/cluster_eval_wc",
  "log_level": "info",
  "transfer": true,
  "placement_policy": "pack",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "load",
      "placement": "all",
      "deps": [],
      "kind": {
        "Input": {
          "path": "TestData/corpus_large.txt",
          "prefetch": true
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "distribute",
      "placement": "all",
      "deps": [
        "load"
      ],
      "kind": {
        "Func": {
          "func": "wc_distribute",
          "out_base": 50
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "map_n",
      "placement": "all",
      "fanout": 8,
      "deps": [
        "distribute"
      ],
      "kind": {
        "Func": {
          "func": "wc_map",
          "output_offset": 100
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "aggregate",
      "placement": "all",
      "deps": [
        "map_n"
      ],
      "kind": {
        "Aggregate": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "aggregate_global",
      "deps": [
        "aggregate"
      ],
      "kind": {
        "Aggregate": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "reduce",
      "deps": [
        "aggregate_global"
      ],
      "kind": {
        "Func": {
          "func": "wc_reduce"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "save",
      "deps": [
        "reduce"
      ],
      "kind": {
        "Output": {
          "path": "TestOutput/cluster_eval_result.txt"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}